high_descs: Walk forward to the microwave on the counter
Open the microwave and remove the red apple from it
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink
Wash the apple under water in the sink then remove it
Turn around and walk over to the round wooden table near the door
Put the apple down on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the washed apple on the table

high_descs: Walk to the microwave in front of you.
Open the microwave door, take the apple out of the microwave, and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Place the apple in the sink to the left of the green sponge, turn the water on, rinse off the apple, turn the water off, pick up the apple from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the wooden table with the coffee maker.
Place the apple down on the table to the left of the fork.
anns.task_desc: To rinse an apple and place it on the wooden table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk a few steps, then turn left to head over to the microwave.
Take the apple out of the microwave.
Turn completely around, walk forward, hanging a left right before reaching the kitchen table, then walk up to the kitchen sink.
Rinse off the apple in the kitchen sink before taking it back out.
Turn around and walk over to the round kitchen table.
Place the apple down on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: Move a clean apple to the kitchen table.
